data.description: Beautiful and Stately corner property with large fenced backyard and double size deck. Home remodeled in 2014 including: new kitchen solid wood cabinets, 2" granite countertops, subway backsplash, appliances, flooring, carpets, hot water tank, new toilets.  New central heat and air installed in 2018.  Roof replaced in 2017. Piers by Power Lift in 2014 with lifetime warranty. All 5 bedrooms are upstairs.  All have great closet sizes. Half bath is downstairs. Dedicated laundry room with plenty of storage.   2 Large living rooms downstairs and 2 dining areas.  Fence 2016.  If you need space, you can't beat this!  Convenient location.  Edmond Schools.  NICE!!
